explanations: 2 comes after 1 in the sequence of natural numbers.
5 is the last number when counting up to 5.
6 comes before 7 in the sequence of natural numbers.
If you have 5 apples and eat 2, you are left with 3.

49 comes before 50 in the sequence of natural numbers.
